cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - This paper deals with machine translation, which falls under the scope of cs.CL.
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper also involves the use of pretrained convolutional neural networks to obtain visual features, which is a common technique in computer vision.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new model for machine translation, which involves the use of attention mechanisms and deep learning techniques, falling under the scope of cs.LG.
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves the use of deep learning techniques and attention mechanisms, which are common in the field of AI.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with multimodal machine translation, which involves the use of both text and images, falling under the scope of cs.MM.
